<plot>Flapjack finds Peppermint Larry sending message to a ship off coast using signal flags. As Peppermint Larry steps out to have lunch, Flapjack takes the flag and waves it endlessly, resulting in a ship off coast sinking, and the rescue boat sinking afterwords. After seeing what have happened Flapjack vowed to never wave a flag again. Just then Captain K'Nuckles comes by. Flapjack waves "hi" to him...using one of the flags. As a result the entire Stormalong Harbor sinks.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?196864</url></doc>
